# Project Structure

## Key Directories
- `internal/app/` - Dependency injection container
- `internal/ecs/core/` - Components and queries
- `internal/ecs/systems/` - Game systems (collision, enemy, health, movement, weapon)
- `internal/ecs/managers/` - Resource, score, level, game state managers
- `internal/scenes/` - Scene implementations and registry
- `internal/game/` - Main game loop and initialization
- `assets/` - Sprites, fonts, entities JSON, levels JSON

## Adding New Features
- **Component**: `ecs/core/components.go`
- **System**: `internal/ecs/systems/<name>/`, init in `game/init_systems.go`
- **Scene**: `internal/scenes/<name>/`, register in `scenes/registry.go`
- **Sprite**: `assets/sprites/`, configure in `ecs/managers/resource/sprite_creation.go`
- **Audio**: `assets/sounds/`, configure in `ecs/managers/resource/audio.go`

## Configuration Files
- `config/constants.go` - Game-wide constants
- `ecs/constants.go` - ECS-specific constants
- `assets/entities/*.json` - Entity definitions
- `assets/levels/*.json` - Level definitions
